ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectFramework Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of the United States of America for Cooperation in the Exploration and Use of Outer Space for Peaceful Purposes
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the Framework Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of the United States of America for COOPERATION IN THE EXPLORATION AND USE OF OUTER SPACE FOR PEACEFUL PURPPOSES.
